🌸友善聊天，不談Zheng zhi
好好聊天歐，我們都是文明人
⚠️本人只有一個號，私信你們的都是騙子！！

{"cid":"1665953433364487","cha_name":"拳皇直播","desc":"美国波士顿，能够进入异次元解封八歧大蛇的三神器八尺琼勾玉、八咫镜和草稚剑正在展出，中情局特工不知火舞正从八神家族传人八神庵处打探三神器的秘密，岂料卢卡尔抢走三神器抢走并躲入了异次元。\n神乐家族传人千鹤透露被抢走的草雉剑为假，委托不知火舞向草稚家族求助。卢卡尔抢走神器后诱骗KOF大赛的格斗家们进入异次元，意欲成为拳皇。\n同时不知火舞和八神庵邀请草稚京一同出战打败卢卡尔。中情局为了调查这起异次元中的犯罪行为亦派出探员特瑞与不知火舞等人一起进入异次元。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1665953433364487","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_
